[32m│[0m    - Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. **Persistent 400 Error**: Despite sending correctly formatted HTTP        [32m│[0m
