[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. **Application Stack**: Werkzeug/3.0.6 Python/3.8.20 (Flask application)   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **Possible Causes:**                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The consistent 400 errors suggest:                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Session/Cookie requirement**: The application might require a session    [32m│[0m
