[32m│[0m 64 bytes from 127.0.0.1: icmp_seq=2 ttl=64 time=0.034 ms                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m --- 127.0.0.1 ping statistics ---                                            [32m│[0m
